---
title: Japanese Beef Tacos with Quick-Pickled Cucumber & Toasted Sesame Seeds
description: Tender beef strips get an aromatic boost in these speedy tacos inspired by Japanese flavours. With a crisp slaw, nutty sesame seeds and lightly pickled cucumber to bring it all together, these are a fusion of some of the tastiest flavours around!
